expected_output: Martin Welcker joined codecentric Leipzig on January 1, 2022. He can be bribed with a good view and delicious food during long trekking tours.

Global expansion of Cody McCodeface could enhance employee participation by providing more opportunities for international colleagues to invest and benefit from the program. This increased participation may drive up demand for the company's shares, potentially improving stock performance. Additionally, a broader market presence could contribute to the overall growth and value of codecentric AG, further benefiting current and future shareholders.

The premium system at codecentric AG, implemented on April 1, 2011, rewards exceptional individual and team achievements. The most recent details on this system, as of August 2023, can be found in the provided document [here](https://confluence.codecentric.de/download/attachments/222141606/UR%20Pra%CC%88mienregelung%2010.0%20-%202023%20%20signed.pdf?version=1&modificationDate=1695396693111&api=v2).
